A joyful person sitting cross-legged on a cozy armchair, bathed in warm golden lamplight, holding a steaming mug while looking at a glowing laptop screen with an expression of genuine delight and surprise. The scene is rendered in Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures, gentle shadows, and whimsical details like floating dust motes catching the light. The room has a lived-in feeling with stacks of notebooks, a trailing houseplant on a nearby shelf, and rain gently streaking down a window in the background. The color palette features warm ambers, soft creams, and touches of deep teal, creating an intimate atmosphere of a quiet personal victory moment discovered late at night.
